### Optional microtightening (good for 325px)
If you want to trim even more around list items in assistant responses:

```css
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .message.assistant ul {
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  .message.assistant li {
    padding-left: 14px;
  }
}
```

